    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You briefly transform your features into the horrific visage of a hag, striking fear into your enemies. Foes in the area must attempt a Will save.</p>\r<p>\n<hr><b>Success</b>  The foe is unaffected.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Failure</b>  The foe is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened} 1.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Critical Failure</b>  The foe is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened} 2.</p>\r<p>\n<hr><b>Heightened (5th)</b>  Foes in the area are @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened} 1 on a success, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened} 2 on a failure, and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened} 3 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.sDPxOjQ9kx2RZE8D]{Fleeing} for 1 round on a critical failure. They are still unaffected on a critical success.</p>",
